    <string>WagerProof uses this to deliver more relevant content and measure the performance of our features.</string>
    <key>NSCameraUsageDescription</key>
    <string>WagerProof needs camera access to upload a profile photo for your agents.</string>
    <key>NSMicrophoneUsageDescription</key>
    <string>WagerProof needs microphone access to power voice chat with WagerBot.</string>
    <key>NSPhotoLibraryUsageDescription</key>
    <string>WagerProof needs photo library access so you can pick a profile image for your agents.</string>
    <key>NSSpeechRecognitionUsageDescription</key>
    <string>WagerProof uses speech recognition to transcribe your voice questions for WagerBot.</string>
